These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend
1. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the blend-smoker is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Cigar     | blend    | bongani   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: rome, san-francisco
2 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | san-francisco | rome        |
| Pet      | hamster  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, helicopter
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, oliveros
1. the vegafina-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Transport   | helicopter    | van |
| Cigar   | vegafina | oliveros |

