The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Pet       | frog | lizard  |
| Hobby   | drawing  | rock-climbing |

